{"tid":216880,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"柴油車真係唔環保？？","createTime":"2017-04-25T13:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T02:22:37.000Z","uid":73118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8cf16cecb17ea5c41f3f096e9eff2b816667d9","tid":216880,"uid":73118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:19:10.000Z","msg":"有一點小弟我唔太明白，上網睇D人話其實柴油車係環保D係咪堅，但係垃圾港府就.&hellip;&hellip;而且突然諗到一點，以相同公里數之下，柴油車用油少過汽油車咁都唔環保？"},{"pid":"f817bd63c2affee14f50e58e4e833770dbe69da6","tid":216880,"uid":30644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:41:28.000Z","msg":"限制私家車增長"},{"pid":"1d028dd95a2cc49302a00a4622d34dd2874e38e7","tid":216880,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:43:14.000Z","msg":"理論上係睇排放污染物<br />\n<br />\n實除上係睇高官個腦"},{"pid":"885d7f46f1d6611404a20f9356ab8373a1d9a0e2","tid":216880,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"堆廿年老賓、馬其實仲加唔環保"},{"pid":"38747dd007fad7da8294ccda36c8d26fd931bb3d","tid":216880,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限"},{"pid":"fd12b085d792e92e603cdd4439e9241bbfbe2d3f","tid":216880,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>堆廿年老賓、馬其實仲加唔環保</blockquote><br />\n可惜柴電車少"},{"pid":"975c40dd5f8ae5b1ddc852a11d6b6208015603b2","tid":216880,"uid":32013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理論上係睇排放污染物<br />\n<br />\n實除上係睇高官個腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n政府取締柴油車入口當然有稅收考量<br />\n但柴油車氮氧化物較汽油車高亦是難以解決的問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492b8cd92fa5bb4bdcb362433cb6632f8c1e47ab","tid":216880,"uid":73118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用電咪又燒煤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbde1387909c4969a1d229dccef55d9a07e2c6c","tid":216880,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用電咪又燒煤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以呢? <br />\n而家係咪要個個post反駁"},{"pid":"46de2dddae9d2ba66b7a938b4ca5ad7f2acbcb24","tid":216880,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直以為環保d 添，屌我仲要兩部車都係柴油版"},{"pid":"663f2b1eefa4ad5a7ad781218831fe9df52961a0","tid":216880,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用電咪又燒煤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中央處理污染嘛，同埋現階段電力係產能過剩，就算唔叉電車啲電依然係浪費左，咁不如善用好過。"},{"pid":"98a4cb95ebf3a1ae39837d36dccabc3c278a66cc","tid":216880,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"用果條乜鳩加州例<br />\n變左好多柴車唔入得"},{"pid":"da7d11862e0756a27ea35b871aa685bfdcfe4bbe","tid":216880,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直以為環保d 添，屌我仲要兩部車都係柴油版</blockquote><br />\n柴油車二氧化碳同非甲烷烴排放低過汽油車<br />\n<a href=\"https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blockDieselCar.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjackyhtlim.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F02%2FblockDieselCar.html%3Fm%3D1&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6c909d0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blockDieselCar.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"b6fb6a9247d8be7913a7cfd45b52481b5a75b90e","tid":216880,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用電咪又燒煤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用電動車最大好處係集中排放，廢氣處理<br />\n講efficiency可能真係唔及普通燃料車<br />\n但係可以解決好多空氣污染，尤其是係社區空氣污染問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實啲污糟燃料掘咗出嚟始終都係會俾人用，不過係你見唔到嘅地方咁解啫，例如遠程船都係會燒重油，就到岸先會轉啲乾淨啲嘅燃料"},{"pid":"b582621b0477dea08cb1d0d43e1ab1d3ea127363","tid":216880,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直以為環保d 添，屌我仲要兩部車都係柴油版</blockquote><br />\n一樣係tie-break個問題, 睇情況<br />\n<br />\n1. 重型車冇得揀低扭力嘅SI一定要揀笨重嘅CI引擎之外, 架車個效率又真係高過用私家車, 慳油之餘減排措施(eg 尿素, filter)勁過柴油私家車所以污柒少咗 <br />\n2. 柴油私家車喺柴油引擎堆性能限制之上受引擎重量同私家車使用方式影響令高效率同慳油嘅特色彌補唔到佢冇汽油引擎咁少污染嘅缺點   <br />\n3. 本身而言, 柴油引擎少咗啲碳排放, 汽油引擎少至少幾倍空氣污染, 你關心空氣污染定氣候變化都好, 柴油私家車減低温室氣體嘅地方比起佢增加空氣污染物嘅大禍唔化算 <br />\n<br />\n慳油至上唔理價錢(非成本)同環境嘅咪柴油車, 想環保揀返汽油車同混能車先啦 <br />\n<br />\n而家話就話兩邊引擎進步緊, 多咗柴電車(主要講 series hybrid 柴電火車嗰隻, RExBEV應該有用柴油發電機嘅)同研究混合兩者長處嘅柴油引擎(汽油引擎亦有學柴油引擎)始終未動搖到汽油引擎喺私家車個地位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依賴交通工具, 唔熟車同ME"},{"pid":"1f89b54589350440cd77e6492f8e5f9aaddf962b","tid":216880,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直以為環保d 添，屌我仲要兩部車都係柴油版</blockquote><br />\n柴油車二氧化碳同非甲烷烴排放低過汽油車<br />\n<a href=\"https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blockDieselCar.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjackyhtlim.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F02%2FblockDieselCar.html%3Fm%3D1&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6c909d0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blockDieselCar.html?m=1</a></blockquote><br />\n林生講空氣污染有冇講柴油車減排個 lifecycle emission同pollution 喺點? 私家車度我唔信服"},{"pid":"80fc0aec0a86e60946d486d81f73180ac3c1b58d","tid":216880,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家車轉做電池車為主嘅電動車符合趨勢, 商用車重用車不在此限</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直以為環保d 添，屌我仲要兩部車都係柴油版</blockquote><br />\n柴油車二氧化碳同非甲烷烴排放低過汽油車<br />\n<a href=\"https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blockDieselCar.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjackyhtlim.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F02%2FblockDieselCar.html%3Fm%3D1&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6c909d0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.hk/2017/02/blockDieselCar.html?m=1</a></blockquote><br />\n林生講空氣污染有冇講柴油車減排個 lifecycle emission同pollution 喺點? 私家車度我唔信服 <br />\n你確保到個個減排合規格同定時換我都唔多覺現時柴油私家車個remedy係值得,<br />\n 縱使我自己亦鍾意柴油車 </blockquote>"},{"pid":"7286d93a5efd5d4c283e192405e93a1ef3ba7812","tid":216880,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1. 用油少=/=污柒少  <br />\n2. 柴油車個未來在柴油引擎可用嘅替代燃料, 目前未跑出  <br />\n3. 私家